<div id="titleDidYouKnow" class="article">
    <span class=rightcornerlink >
            <a href="/register/login?why=edit&ref_=tt_trv_trv" rel="login">Edit</a>
    </span>
    <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
    <div id="trivia" class="txt-block">
        <h4>Trivia</h4>


<a href="/name/nm0000277/?ref_=tt_trv_trv">Richard Attenborough</a> and his wife <a href="/name/nm0799257/?ref_=tt_trv_trv">Sheila Sim</a> owned a share of the rights in Britain's longest-running play "The Mousetrap" which they sold to fund the production of this movie.        <a href="trivia?ref_=tt_trv_trv" class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>
            <hr />
     <div id="goofs"  class="txt-block">
        <h4>Goofs</h4>
Lord Irwin, in real life, was born with a withered left arm with no hand. However, he is shown several times in the movie with both a left and right hand.        <a href="trivia?tab=gf&ref_=tt_trv_gf" class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>   
            <hr />
    <div id="quotes" class="text-block">
        <h4>Quotes</h4>
[<span class="fine">first lines</span>]
<br /><span class="character">Hindu</span>:
He will be saying prayers in the garden. Just follow the others.
<br />        <a href="trivia?tab=qt&ref_=tt_trv_qu" class="nobr" >See more</a> &raquo;
    </div>
            <hr />
    <div id="connections" class="text-block">
        <h4>Connections</h4>
        Referenced in <a href="/title/tt0102032/?ref_=tt_trv_cnn">High Strung</a>&nbsp;(1991)

<br />Thane references the fast of Gandhi.
        <a href="trivia?tab=mc&ref_=tt_trv_cnn" class="nobr" >See more</a> &raquo;
    </div>
            <hr />
    <div id="soundtracks" class="text-block">
        <h4>Soundtracks</h4>
            "God Save the King!"<br />
                (1744) (uncredited)<br />
                Music attributed to <a href="/name/nm0136963/?ref_=tt_trv_snd">Henry Carey</a><br />
                Sung by <a href="/name/nm0001426/?ref_=tt_trv_snd">Ben Kingsley</a><br />
                Reprised when India achieves independence<br />
        <a href="soundtrack?ref_=tt_trv_snd" class="nobr" >See more</a> &raquo;
    </div>
</div>
